Charset / iconv: the build uses WITH_ICONV=0. GNU libiconv is NOT present in
the binary or the distribution. libxml2 uses musl/Emscripten libc's built-in
iconv; PHP's ext/iconv (iconv(), iconv_strlen(), etc.) is not compiled.
See docs/DECISIONS.md ADR-0011 for the full analysis, including the
correction of the Session 1 audit error (libiconv was misidentified as
statically linked; it was in fact an optional WASM side module).

GPL components are excluded from the link: readline (GPL) is confirmed absent
from this build (no libreadline in the link set). See docs/DECISIONS.md
ADR-0001 and ADR-0003.

No LGPL components are present in the statically-linked binary or the
distributed build artifacts. The ADR-0001 LGPL concern is resolved.

